Ponnur Hills is an area in Tiruvannamalai district of Tamil Nadu. It is the place were Kunda Kunda, the Digambar Jain Acharya ( Principal Monk ) spent a lot of time. It is believed that he visited Videha Kshetra and ascended to [[Heaven]] from here.

